- content_for :page_title, "Thank you for backing PlanningAlerts"

.donations-page.donations-thankyou
  .container.main
    #content
      %h1.page-title Thank you for backing PlanningAlerts!
      %p
        %strong We’re processing your donation and will send through a receipt shortly.
      %p
        Your donations go to informing more people about local planning
        and giving them a chance to participate.
        With the backing of people like you we’ve sent out
        - cache "donations_create_stats", expires_in: 1.hour do
          = number_with_delimiter(EmailBatch.total_sent_in_past_week)
        PlanningAlerts emails to people in the last 7 days.
      %p
        You can cancel your monthly donations at any time, just
        #{mail_to "contact@planningalerts.org.au", "email us at contact@planningalerts.org.au"}.
